29
00:00:20,840 --> 00:00:21,920
Sin mojarse.

30
00:00:21,920 --> 00:00:23,320
Sin estropearse.

31
00:00:23,320 --> 00:00:23,960
¿Sabéis qué

32
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:24,280
