41
00:00:30,520 --> 00:00:31,560
Y fijaos...

42
00:00:31,560 --> 00:00:31,720
a los

43
00:00:31,720 --> 00:00:32,360
pocos minutos,

44
00:00:32,360 --> 00:00:32,680
alguien de

45
00:00:32,680 --> 00:00:33,040
la app

46
00:00:33,040 --> 00:00:33,600
ya vino

47
00:00:33,600 --> 00:00:34,320
a recogerla.

48
00:00:34,320 --> 00:00:35,240
Minutos.

49
00:00:35,240 --> 00:00:36,280
No horas.

50
00:00:36,280 --> 00:00:37,200
Minutos.

51
00:00:37,200 --> 00:00:37,760
Eso demuestra

52
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:38,160
