62
00:00:44,080 --> 00:00:44,880
Entero.

63
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:45,280
Limpio.

64
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:46,320
Cada paseo

65
00:00:46,320 --> 00:00:47,560
